FBIS4-58701 "drnes088dd_94002" FBIS-NES-94-088 Daily Report 5 May 1994 Palestinian Affairs Al-Husayni Put in Charge of `Jerusalem Portfolio' Al-Husayni Put in Charge of `Jerusalem Portfolio' TA0505172894 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 1500 GMT 5 May 94 TA0505172894 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el English BFN [Text] In Jerusalem, Palestinian leader Faysal al-Husayni says he has been appointed to take charge of the Jerusalem portfolio on behalf of the PLO. He said he did not take part in yesterday's signing ceremony for two reasons. He had hoped the accord would be more positive, and he was busy at work.
